{
  "texts": [
    "Models are tasked with choosing the correct causal relationship based on provided premises.",
    "Incorporated into SuperGLUE, COPA serves as an assessment benchmark for English NLU tasks.",
    "• CREAK (Onoe et al, 2021).",
    "For the exploration of models' abilities to amalgamate entity knowledge with common-sense reasoning, the CREAK dataset is introduced.",
    "It establishes a connection between factual details about entities (e.g., wizards like Harry Potter, proficient in broomstick flying) and commonsense reasoning principles (e.g., having expertise in a skill allows one to instruct others)."
  ]
}